    "Communication:Effective communication plays a crucial role of in bridging the gap between signers and nonsigners.",
    "To achieve bidirectional communication between sign language users (signers) and those who do not use sign language (non-signers), it is essential to provide effective translation features from sign language to spoken language and vice versa.",
    "This can be achieved by integrating sign language recognition technology and text-to-sign conversion systems.",
    "Additionally, offering options for real-time or recorded video can enhance the intuitiveness and interactivity of communication.Education: recognising the distinct needs of adult and child learners, our APP provides tailored educational experiences.",
    "For adults, we offer a comprehensive dictionary, adaptive pacing, and resources like self-study modules and interactive exercises."
